title: Fed will hike rates three times this year, as expected, says Fiduciary Trust's Carin Pai
text:
Fed will hike rates three times this year, as expected, says Fiduciary Trust's Carin Pai 6:39am IST - 06:55 
Fed's decision today will probably keep the rising yields in Treasuries not too rampant, says Carin Pai, EVP and Head of Equity Strategy at Fiduciary Trust Company International. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
